problem: Is Olympia, Washington part of "Ish river country"?
gt_solution:
Poet Robert Sund called the Puget Sound region "Ish River country".
Olympia is in the Puget Sound region.
facts: Poet Robert Sund called the Puget Sound region "Ish River country".
